help but...

29:20.493 --> 29:23.393
You might wanna add bridgette
to your list of 99 problems

29:23.496 --> 29:26.163
'cause she is feeling
some type of way, girl.

29:26.866 --> 29:29.082
Yeah. Come on.

29:31.537 --> 29:32.586
Thank you.

29:35.674 --> 29:37.240
-[sighs]
-you feel better now?

29:37.343 --> 29:39.242
We have the entire vineyard,

29:39.345 --> 29:41.962
