facility and the offices

29:42.047 --> 29:43.263
outfitted with
the latest tech.

29:43.382 --> 29:45.349
Whoever this extortionist is,

29:45.434 --> 29:48.268
is no match for this
tiger mom.

29:48.387 --> 29:50.854
I don't know. Maybe we should
lay low for a bit.

29:50.940 --> 29:53.474
-Get out of town.
Let this thing blow over.
-[vanessa] no.

29:53.559 --> 29:55.926
We are facing this thing
head on.

29:56.028 --> 29:59.530
Dana, get your little pi to
look into why your father had
all those passports for us.

29:59.615 --> 30:02.533
-[phone ringing]
-dana thinks it's some sort of
crime syndicate.

30:02.618 --> 30:04.368
-Right, babe?
-[dana] plot twist.

30:04.453 --> 30:07.654
