to kill the<i> asset makers</i> story

30:18.384 --> 30:20.283
and wipe the sd card
of your interview.

30:20.386 --> 30:23.620
As if it was my fault
that you one percent-ers
are dysfunctional.

30:23.722 --> 30:27.641
I just called an old friend
who would hate to see
a two-bit muckraker

30:27.760 --> 30:29.626
drown our good names
in the mud.

30:29.728 --> 30:32.980
-You can't control the story.
-Sure, we can.

30:33.098 --> 30:35.065
We didn't make all this money
for nothing.

30:35.150 --> 30:37.067
-Listen, lisa, is it?
-Yeah.

30:37.152 --> 30:41.488
Remember how you came in?
Well, you can go out
the exact same way.

30:41.607 --> 30:43.156
Unbelievable.

30:43.275 --> 30:45.609
-Bye, 99 percent-er.
-[chuckles]

30:46.996 --> 30:48.579
you called the board?

30:49.448 --> 30:50.313
For me?

30:50.416 --> 30:52.833
Dana, this housewife
has got your back.

30:54.119 --> 30:56.620
-I don't understand.
You didn't know?
-No.

30:58.290 --> 30:59.256
Honey.

31:00.426 --> 31:02.759
Just sit for a minute, please.
Please.

31:06.599 --> 31:08.682
What your aunt yvette said

31:09.602 --> 31:10.517
is true.

31:11.854 --> 31:15.171
When we saw your little body
on that ultrasound,

31:15.274 --> 31:18.308
I couldn't bear the thought
of you having a hard life.

31:18.811 --> 31:21.528
But I chose to have you.

31:21.647 --> 31:24.281
'cause my baby boy was
gonna grow up to be a king.

31:24.984 --> 31:26.950
And I'd make sure of it.

31:27.036 --> 31:31.071
