a random housewife.
-[chuckles] it's okay, honey.

31:31.156 --> 31:34.024
And listen, it was your father
who called cambridge sloan

31:34.126 --> 31:35.876
and told them not to
give you the job.

31:35.995 --> 31:37.861
He wanted you here with us.

31:37.963 --> 31:41.698
Because he knew your
brilliance was needed
at the house of kings.

31:41.800 --> 31:43.033
Why didn't you tell me?

31:43.135 --> 31:45.719
Dana, I don't know.

31:45.838 --> 31:49.890
In fact, the more I think
I know about your father,
the less I do.

31:50.843 --> 31:52.375
Now,

31:52.478 --> 31:57.047
promise me that you will
never trust your
aunt melanie again.

31:57.149 --> 31:59.215
Honey, if you want the truth,
I am your mom.

31:59.318 --> 32:01.151
