Bridgette just called.

32:32.184 --> 32:34.635
The extortionist poisoned
shawn and shawn's vines
with glyphosate.

32:34.720 --> 32:37.638
-The weed killer?
-Extortionist?

32:37.723 --> 32:40.423
Wait, that's insane.
Glyphosate will ruin the vines

32:40.526 --> 32:42.258
and the entire vineyard
will be destroyed.

32:42.361 --> 32:44.928
-Are we sure--
-I'm not waiting for your
permission, August.

32:45.030 --> 32:48.315
Otis has $50,000 in an account
that is unexplained

32:48.400 --> 32:50.117
and an $80,000 boat.

32:50.235 --> 32:52.869
He had beef with our dad
and he worked
at both vineyards.

32:52.955 --> 32:54.121
He's our guy.

32:56.241 --> 32:57.941
[line ringing]

32:58.043 --> 32:59.609
the chicken's come home
to roost.

32:59.712 --> 33:01.578
[policeman] otis haney,
you are under arrest.

33:03.465 --> 33:04.781
Otis, don't!

33:04.883 --> 33:06.917
[policeman] I need
a backup car at the west
entrance right now.

33:11.807 --> 33:13.423
[tires screech, crashing]

33:15.811 --> 33:18.695
you were right.
Mom just got off the phone
with the hospital and...

33:19.732 --> 33:21.481
Otis is still
unconscious but...

33:23.369 --> 33:24.568
The way he ran

33:26.538 --> 33:27.954
just seems like he's guilty.

33:30.626 --> 33:32.459
I dragged my feet
and you acted.

33:33.212 --> 33:34.077
You forced my hand.

33:36.465 --> 33:37.464
I'm grateful, dana.

33:39.802 --> 33:42.719
You protected my vision
better than I did, and...

33:44.256 --> 33:46.506
It's gonna take both of us
to keep dad's dream alive.

33:51.897 --> 33:55.232
I can't believe otis
just ran from the police.

33:55.317 --> 33:57.300
Guilt'll make you do
some crazy shit.

33:57.403 --> 33:59.853
Yeah, but what was he saying
to dad to make him wanna flee
the country

33:59.938 --> 34:01.805
like he was in some
denzel movie.

34:01.907 --> 34:03.573
I don't know.

34:03.659 --> 34:06.526
-Money breeds desperation.
-Well, all I know

34:06.612 --> 34:08.111
is my husband's a hero.

34:10.449 --> 34:15.619
Dana, you bossed up today
like a true king and a saint.

34:15.704 --> 34:18.588
Thank you for protecting
this family and this land.

34:18.674 --> 34:20.757
[all clapping]

34:28.267 --> 34:29.933
you don't have to walk me out.

34:30.018 --> 34:32.686
I owe you for telling us
about shawn and shawn.

34:33.972 --> 34:36.139
Who else knows what else
otis could've done.

34:36.225 --> 34:39.509
But why'd you tell dana
and not me?

34:39.611 --> 34:42.112
I mean how long are you
gonna be pissed at me?

34:42.197 --> 34:45.348
August, you blocked me from
getting my job back
but dana supported me?

34:45.451 --> 34:47.784
Dana's playing both sides
of the fence, you know this.

34:47.870 --> 34:50.237
You used to put
friendship first.

34:50.322 --> 34:53.690
You used to do the right thing
because it was right.

34:53.792 --> 34:55.692
Now, you're just about
the company's bottom line.

34:55.794 --> 34:58.128
You think I don't know
your value?

34:58.213 --> 35:01.465
It kills me that I forced you
to work at our competitor.

35:01.550 --> 35:04.634
But you and me,
we can work through this.

35:04.720 --> 35:06.586
I'm almost on the brink
of a nervous breakdown.

35:06.672 --> 35:08.705
I have to think about
the whole picture.

35:08.807 --> 35:09.589
Like, I...

35:11.093 --> 35:13.393
I know I sacrificed
our relationship for her
and...

35:14.980 --> 35:16.596
I hate that.

35:16.682 --> 35:20.016
I hate that I did this to
my friend, to my sister.

35:22.571 --> 35:25.489
But I'm just trying to pick up
the pieces that dad shattered.

35:25.574 --> 35:27.858
So, I'm gonna ask you
point blank,

35:28.861 --> 35:31.895
do you think that we could...

35:31.997 --> 35:34.197
Press a reset button
on our relationship?

35:34.917 --> 35:36.249
Is that possible?

35:38.036 --> 35:39.503
I'm not making any promises.

35:41.456 --> 35:42.539
But I'll try.

35:50.048 --> 35:51.080
[door shuts]

35:51.183 --> 35:54.351
<i> ♪ how do I step</i>
<i> at the house I be working ♪</i>

