36:40.265 --> 36:41.398
I'm sorry.

36:41.483 --> 36:43.433
I've never been with anyone
who had kids before.

36:43.518 --> 36:45.268
And I forget you have a...

36:46.238 --> 36:47.687
Little one sometimes.

36:47.773 --> 36:50.357
-He's pretty fantastic. Yeah.
-[August laughs]

36:50.442 --> 36:52.642
just hope he's something
you're okay with.

36:52.744 --> 36:55.745
-I mean, this dating thing
is new to me.
-Yeah, no.

36:55.831 --> 36:57.697
It's fine. I...

36:57.783 --> 37:00.867
Honestly, I'm just more
confused about us.

37:00.953 --> 37:03.086
-Hm.
-I mean,

37:04.172 --> 37:05.255
are we dating?

37:06.258 --> 37:08.508
'cause you haven't made
a move and we've...

37:09.511 --> 37:11.211
Been together before.

37:11.296 --> 37:13.096
-Hm.
-Is it your marriage?

37:14.049 --> 37:14.998
No.

37:15.100 --> 37:17.500
The divorce is definitely
in process.

37:17.603 --> 37:19.168
It's just that...

37:19.271 --> 37:22.472
We're not teenagers anymore
and I wanna make sure that
it's real this time.

37:23.275 --> 37:24.441
What was it the last time?

37:25.560 --> 37:26.726
It wasn't just about us.

37:29.531 --> 37:30.730
You did so much for me.

37:32.067 --> 37:33.984
You told your parents
what I was dealing with.

37:34.987 --> 37:36.202
The abuse.

37:38.040 --> 37:39.789
I mean, they pulled me
out of foster care

37:39.875 --> 37:41.625
found me a place
to stay senior year.

37:42.961 --> 37:45.695
You aren't just my girlfriend,
you are my savior.

37:45.797 --> 37:46.713
[August chuckles softly]

37:52.387 --> 37:53.470
and...

37:53.555 --> 37:55.305
As grateful as I was for you,

37:56.308 --> 37:57.641
as I am to you,

37:57.726 --> 37:59.092
I felt like I owed you.

38:00.512 --> 38:03.680
It was hard for a 17-year-old
to feel all those feelings.

38:05.434 --> 38:07.317
I didn't wanna be with you
because I felt I had to.

38:07.402 --> 38:10.487
I wanted to be with you
because I wanted to.

38:11.073 --> 38:13.056
