like I was using you.

38:19.081 --> 38:20.113
Or your family.

38:22.918 --> 38:26.836
I mean, harvard was far
but I got myself a full ride.

38:26.922 --> 38:28.421
-I got to grow up.
-Mm-hm.

38:29.174 --> 38:30.740
Be my own man.

38:30.842 --> 38:33.793
Well, you did it, kelvin.

38:33.879 --> 38:37.297
And you don't owe me,
or my family, anything.

38:44.656 --> 38:47.490
-You know, even when we were
seeing other people...
-Hm.

38:48.660 --> 38:49.993
I always thought about you.

38:52.748 --> 38:56.166
I always loved you for you.

38:57.335 --> 38:59.202
Not for what you did,

38:59.304 --> 39:01.921
or for your parents
or for that vineyard.

39:02.841 --> 39:03.973
But for you.

39:06.178 --> 39:08.344
You know? And when I realized
that you'd moved on,

39:09.097 --> 39:10.597
I married sonya.

