39:48.186 --> 39:51.420
-I'm trying to step up.
-Where's the cheat sheet
you carry around?

39:51.523 --> 39:53.273
Shit, I'm gonna go
grab that right now.

39:53.391 --> 39:55.141
Appreciate you, bro.
Be right back.

40:00.732 --> 40:03.566
